snippet.title: Insurance for Surrogacy: What you Need to Know with with Erica - Facebook Live 2/22/19
snippet.description: President of Growing Generations, Erica Horton, discusses the importance of insurance in surrogacy. As an intended parent or surrogate, insurance plays a vital role in your journey. In this live broadcast, Erica provides an overview of common insurance options, offers helpful tips, and hosts a general Q & A on the topic.
